🖥 Installation
1️⃣ Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/YOURNAME/secure-ai-gateway.git

cd secure-ai-gateway

🐍 Python Environment (local dev)
python -m venv venv

source venv/bin/activate
Windows
venv\Scripts\activate

🧠 Install Ollama (optional local LLM)
https://ollama.com
Pull model
ollama pull llama3
Run
ollama run llama3

🐳 Build Docker Images
docker build -t gateway:latest ./gateway

docker build -t security-agent:latest ./agents

☸️ Deploy to Kubernetes
Create namespaces
kubectl create namespace ai-control

kubectl create namespace ai-agents

kubectl create namespace policy
Deploy OPA
kubectl apply -f kube/opa-policies.yaml

kubectl apply -f kube/opa-deployment.yaml
Deploy agent
kubectl apply -f kube/agent-deployment.yaml
Deploy gateway
kubectl apply -f kube/gateway-deployment.yaml

🧪 Test the System
Port forward gateway
kubectl port-forward svc/gateway 8080:8080 -n ai-control
Query gateway
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/invoke \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{
"user": "security_engineer",
"agent": "security-agent",
"prompt": "Is CVE-2024-1234 affecting our system?"
}'

🔍 Example Response
